[~xuefuz] I attached the jar with both the generic and non-generic functions.
To reproduce:
{code}
set hive.execution.engine=spark;
create function genNth as 'org.example.GenericUDFNth' using jar 'hdfs:///...';
create function nth as 'org.example.UDFNth' using jar 'hdfs:///...';
select distinct nth(1,2,1) from tab;
select distinct genNth(1,2,1) from tab;
{code}
